item.description: Are you are a business professional who markets products or services to other businesses with 10 or more employees? We are a weekly business to business networking group looking to build relationships with like minded business owners and professionals. We are driven by the idea of building relationships with each other so we can exchange referrals and clients. This is not your typical business networking meeting. In order to attend you must derive at least 80% of your business from other businesses. We are industry exclusive so reserve your seat at the table before your competition does.
item.name: Queen City B2B Networking
